[{"tag":"head","title":"公共设施","shareable":true,"contact":true},{"tag":"h3","text":"洗漱区"},{"tag":"p","text":"洗漱区全天供应冷水。生活热水每日使用量固定为18升(新生需要先在生活用水补助机上刷卡进行激活，激活时间略有延时)，超过18升按照￥0.2/升扣除，可以自行到生活用水补助机处充值。寝室楼下就设有生活用水补助机。"},{"tag":"p","head":"热水供应时间","text":"本部校区：\n 5:00-8:00，21:00-23:00\n净月校区：\n6:00-8:00，19:00-22:00(天华公寓全天供应)。"},{"tag":"list","content":[{"text":"如何激活生活用水","aim":"card2","icon":"/icon/guide/card.svg"}]},{"tag":"img","src":"https://pic.kuaizhan.com/g1/M00/91/62/wKjmqVl9hACAR66rAADtC1XuulU0747826/imageView/v1/thumbnail/640x0","desc":"图为本部三舍AB洗漱区"},{"tag":"img","src":"https://pic.kuaizhan.com/g1/M00/91/62/wKjmqVl9g7mAbnfZAACMNWfdtg41656008/imageView/v1/thumbnail/640x0","desc":"图为本部三舍C洗漱区"},{"tag":"img","src":"https://pic.kuaizhan.com/g1/M01/91/62/wKjmqVl9g6CAEI-WAAGVw7uu5Xs1056054/imageView/v1/thumbnail/640x0","desc":"图为净月公寓洗漱区"},{"tag":"p","head":"卫生间","text":"   卫生间处在公共区域，有阿姨定期打扫卫生，很整洁。"},{"tag":"img","src":"https://pic.kuaizhan.com/g1/M01/91/63/wKjmqVl9hXSAOBeAABmrRBrl_Q83881084/imageView/v1/thumbnail/640x0"},{"tag":"img","src":"https://pic.kuaizhan.com/g2/M01/80/96/CgpQVFl9hV-ASgSHAC3XwsJHYhM9384030/imageView/v1/thumbnail/640x0"},{"tag":"p","head":"吹风机","text":"   女生寝室楼每层楼都有一个或两个吹风机，插一卡通就可以使用。"},{"tag":"img","src":"https://pic.kuaizhan.com/g2/M01/80/98/CgpQVFl9iISAW_AWAA3EFjs57wM4349529/imageView/v1/thumbnail/640x0"},{"tag":"p","head":"洗衣机","text":"   洗衣机是单筒洗衣机，可洗可甩干。大部分寝室楼的每个楼层有两个洗衣机(三舍B一台)。洗衣机为刷卡使用。根据所需洗涤方式刷卡，刷卡完毕后将洗衣机盖关闭即可洗衣, 洗衣用的洗衣液或洗衣粉需自己准备，在洗衣前加入洗衣机内。"},{"tag":"img","src":"https://pic.kuaizhan.com/g2/M00/80/98/CgpQVFl9iMaAY6bwAAEyJlHpDXA3713141/imageView/v1/thumbnail/640x0"},{"tag":"p","head":"直饮水机","text":"   刷卡分别可以接冷/常温/热的饮用水，学校每天免费供应90秒使用时长(约2-4升，视直饮机水压)，全天供应。超出部分收取制水成本费用，热水0.3元/升，常温水0.2元/升。直饮水服务所需的额外费用，是使用校园卡小钱包内的余额，师生可以在自助终端机上进行一卡通小钱包充值。"},{"tag":"img","src":"https://pic.kuaizhan.com/g2/M00/82/55/wKjmqll9iROAAyvXAAFvl0L2slU0180058/imageView/v1/thumbnail/640x0"},{"tag":"img","src":"https://pic.kuaizhan.com/g1/M00/91/68/wKjmqVl9ib2ATy4sACjJ4Roa5YQ6686464/imageView/v1/thumbnail/640x0"},{"tag":"p","head":"自习室","text":"   寝室楼内每层均设有自习室。自习室不间断供电。"},{"tag":"img","src":"https://pic.kuaizhan.com/g1/M00/6E/2E/CgpQU1l9jHKAFQ84AAFVHQOisPI2108104/imageView/v1/thumbnail/640x0","desc":"三舍A自习室"},{"tag":"img","src":"https://pic.kuaizhan.com/g1/M01/6E/29/CgpQU1l9iciAdPf6ABhnksBE_IU0815243/imageView/v1/thumbnail/640x0","desc":"三舍B自习室"},{"tag":"img","src":"https://pic.kuaizhan.com/g2/M00/82/5A/wKjmqll9jC-Aa9uaAAG9IJn9V_c5121719/imageView/v1/thumbnail/640x0","desc":"三舍C自习室"},{"tag":"img","src":"https://pic.kuaizhan.com/g1/M01/91/68/wKjmqVl9icmAc7SrAAC8hfsXXwo9367729/imageView/v1/thumbnail/640x0","desc":"天华公寓自习室"},{"tag":"p","head":"电梯","text":"   三舍作为高层建筑，A座、C座拥有四台电梯，B拥有三台电梯，客梯不停低楼层，入住时可以使用货梯。请注意客梯是分为单层客梯和双层客梯的，楼下一楼电梯入口处有明确的指示牌。净月寝室没有电梯。"},{"tag":"img","src":"https://pic.kuaizhan.com/g2/M00/82/5B/wKjmqll9jOGAITeNAAGlLL3dLNI6483845/imageView/v1/thumbnail/640x0","desc":"三舍电梯"},{"tag":"foot","author":"Mr.Hope","time":"2019/2/10"}]